Generic single-database configuration for Alembic migrations.

## Commands

### Generate new migration (autogenerate from models)
Similar to: dotnet ef migrations add InitialCreate
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Initial migration"
```

### Apply migrations to database
Similar to: dotnet ef database update
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback last migration
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history
```

### View current database version
```bash
alembic current
```

### Create empty migration (manual)
```bash
alembic revision -m "add custom logic"
```
